{"tid":369323,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"屌奶星 港鐵又有新優惠","createTime":"2017-08-22T08:43:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T13:37:50.000Z","uid":24685,"like":2,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"19fc61d398b1dd3433123b839b7565c31b4ef2a3","tid":369323,"uid":24685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T08:43:46.000Z","msg":"為慶祝香港回歸20周年，港鐵將今年10月1日（星期日）及2日（星期一）定為車價特惠日，兩日內成人可享小童半價優惠，而小童、長者及傷殘人士則可以1元車費乘搭港鐵，優惠於兩日內不限次數，預計優惠涉及3千萬元。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵主席馬時亨指出，<span style=\"color: red;\">特惠日是為慶祝香港回歸20周年，港鐵以顧客為上，希望乘客搭得開心。</span><br />\n<br />\nd優惠正到 睇完喊左出嚟 攪手只係希望大家搭得開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"669f1fc5c9d645baf7ab8ca60f6518c97c85f205","tid":369323,"uid":31314,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T08:45:05.000Z","msg":"樓主可以用$1搭港鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50a7a3871eff754419f647ceaa5ca17f9840becd","tid":369323,"uid":43825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T08:45:09.000Z","msg":"真係多撚謝哂"},{"pid":"ac2cbde49c08b39a3379d87b52efa41d520c6736","tid":369323,"uid":52839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T08:45:13.000Z","msg":"邊有錢賺呀咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n港鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 良心企業"},{"pid":"8fbb2806cf240e83e379d92c1b97b2ee37243d86","tid":369323,"uid":74085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T08:45:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 皇恩浩蕩"},{"pid":"6975f7503ebc119b4d121540c8e74bc1b2dd9511","tid":369323,"uid":116530,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T08:45:30.000Z","msg":"日日壞車 優惠就得一兩日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":